<li><b>CMI</b>: A paper on the benefits of CMI. <a href="http://clearspider.com/vmipaper/clearspidercmi-2-1.pdf" class="external free" title="http://clearspider.com/vmipaper/clearspidercmi-2-1.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://clearspider.com/vmipaper/clearspidercmi-2-1.pdf</a></li>
</ul>
